snippet.title: Rock of Ages 3 - The Untold Tale of Humpty Dumpty
snippet.description:
Get more Humpty Dumpty action when Rock of Ages 3 launches this June! 
Learn more: http://rockofages3.com

When Humpty Dumpty went for a stroll, what Humpty Dumpty did not then know,
Was that all the king's horses, and all the kings men,
Had a trap for when they saw Humpty Dumpty again.
Now Humpty Dumpty could no longer roll, but Humpty Dumpty had him some pals,
They built up their boulders, and took their own aim,
And crushed the king’s weak defences to win them the game.

Play as Humpty Dumpty and build your own egg-cellent defences when Rock of Ages 3 releases this June!
